  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Inghams strive to share their passion for skiing and snowboarding and want to help as many people onto the slopes as possible so we’ve got a bit creative this season.</p>
<p><br /><strong>Revise and ski</strong><br />Work hard, ski hard- we’ve all heard the saying (almost!) but this Easter Inghams are working in conjunction with Tutor House and Revise and Ski to offer students and families a ski holiday which compliments students’ revision. The Revise and Ski scheme is run by experienced tutors with study sessions aimed at GCSE, AS and A2 students as well as Common Entrance pupils. The well planned sessions focus on exam technique and cover a wide range of subjects. Students will have 22.5 hrs of formal lessons per week leaving plenty of times to explore the slopes!</p>
<p>Make the most of the Revise and Ski scheme in <a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d}" title="Val d'Isere">Val d’Isère</a> one of <a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France’s</a> largest and most loved ski resorts on Inghams’ departures on 19th, 26th March 2016 or 2nd April 2016. For more information visit <a href="http://www.reviseandski.com/inghams/">http://www.reviseandski.com/inghams/</a> or call 01483 791 114 to speak to the Inghams Reservation Team.</p>
<p><a href="/ski-holidays/special-offers"><strong>Ski Again</strong></a><br />We understand that when you’ve got a busy schedule it’s easy to fall off the skiing bandwagon but it’s time to jump back on! Inghams Ski Again programme encourages anyone who has not skied for five years or more to pick it back up. A further bonus, Inghams has <strong>50 free lift passes</strong> on a first come first served basis, subject to qualifying for the offer. <br />Ski Again in Mayrhofen, Austria</p>
<p><br />Inghams is offering 7 nights half board at the 3* <a data-udi="umb://document/9a7847d3d5f440499fa5e4f8403ad726" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9a7847d3d5f440499fa5e4f8403ad726}" title="Hotel Elisabeth-Rose">Hotel Elisabeth-Rose</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a>, Austria from £518 per person, saving £190 per person departing 19th March 2016. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick to Innsbruck and resort transfers. Add the Ski Again package for £166.40 per person which includes a free 6 day lift pass, refresher tuition on 3 days and 6 days ski and boot hire. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk">www.inghams.co.uk</a> or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<p><strong>Ski Again in Obergurgl, Austria</strong><br />Inghams is offering 7 nights, half board at the 4.5* <a data-udi="umb://document/e60e4140f1684d508d02b12990b6014a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e60e4140f1684d508d02b12990b6014a}" title="Hotel Edelweiss &amp; Gurgl">Hotel Edelweiss</a> and Gurgl, Obergurgl, Austria from £988 per person departing 16th April 2016. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick to Innsbruck and resort transfers. Add the Ski Again for £195.20 per person for 6 days free lift pass, refresher ski tuition on 3 days ski school and 6 days ski and boot hire. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk">www.inghams.co.uk</a> or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<p><strong>Ski again in Söll, Austria</strong><br />Inghams is offering 7 nights chalet catering at the 3 diamond <a href="/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/austria/skiwelt-wilder-kaiser-brixental-area/soll">Chalet Bichler</a>,<a href="/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/austria/skiwelt-wilder-kaiser-brixental-area/soll"> Söll,</a> Austria from £499 person, saving £150 person departing 19th March 2016. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick to Salzburg and resort tramsfers. Ski Again from £163.20 per person including a free 6 day lift pass, refreshers ski tuition on 3 days refresher and 6 days of ski and boot hire. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk">www.inghams.co.uk</a> or call 01483791 114. </p>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/special-offers/ski-again">https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/special-offers/ski-again</a></p>
<p><strong>ENDS.</strong></p>
